~ start
if get_parent().will_end_past_midnight:
	Player: I don't have enough time left in the day to {{chore_name}}.
else:
	Player: Hmm... I could {{chore_name}}.
	Player: It'll take me {{time_taken}} hours and earn me {{point_value}} Obedience Points.
	if will_end_past_ten:
		Player: But I'd be staying up past 10PM.
	Player: Should I {{chore_name}}?
	- Yes.
		do chore_completed()
		Player: All done!
	- No.
		Player: Maybe later.
		do deselect()
=> END